{"tid":462931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：反對議員用「赤化」形容中國歷史和國民教育","createTime":"2017-11-09T04:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T04:38:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a763e34bee63a2580c04bbc7ac9031f812d2e65","tid":462931,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1363848-20171109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1363848-20171109.htm&d=jSwC3uiGN3vC7JBO22xqby7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b3342a04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1363848-20171109.htm&h=d45d080a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1363848-20171109.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1363848_1_20171109121816.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1363848_1_20171109121816.jpg&h=ef42d17d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會第二日辯論施政報告致謝議案，早上完成第二節討論人口、教育和青年政策措施。<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄發言時表示，讓學生認識國家歷史、文化、政治體制，培養學生的國家觀念，是學校教育應有之責，希望議員不論政見如何，都不要戴有色眼鏡看待專業教育工作，反對議員用「赤化」這字眼形容中國歷史和國民教育，或者將「愛國」說成政治議題，局方會繼續推行基本法和國民教育。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄說，部分議員擔心他受到外來壓力影響工作，但他指過去幾個月的工作壓力，較多來自立法會議員，及自己對教育工作的承擔。他強調，制定香港教育政策時，只會以香港學生和香港整體利益作為出發點，請議員放心。"},{"pid":"d00477d1e4d8ffb524a6574780c7fe1520fa9dd2","tid":462931,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:26:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"954f7dba5099e74cfdc11708282973544e736b33","tid":462931,"uid":106247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"局長知唔知咩叫言論自由"},{"pid":"31ebb85285bf19aeec0d86246dc212b2ba69fce2","tid":462931,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T04:38:21.000Z","msg":"愛國唔係政治議題唔通係科技議題、工商議題？"}]}